Subject: [PATCH 22/30] v4l2-dv-timings: add v4l2_print_dv_timings helper

commit 0216dc2fe666b5cedba54df4c0be6ddc8eb352e1 upstream

Drivers often have to log the contents of a dv_timings struct. Adding
this helper will make it easier for drivers to do so.

